eve|year=2013|title=Encyclopedia of Great Popular Song Recordings|volume=2|publisher=Scarecrow Press|isbn=978-0-8108-8296-6|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Slaughter|first=Todd|year=2004|title=The Elvis Archives|publisher=Omnibus Press|isbn=1-84449-380-6|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite journal|author=The Discographer staff|year=1971|title=Harmony/Velvetone/Diva Catalogue|journal=The Discographer: A Quarterly Journal for the Discographer and Collector of Americana-musicana|volume=2|number=3|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|author=Whitburn, Joel|year=1996|title=Joel Whitburn's top pop albums, 1955\u20131996|publisher=Record Research, Inc|isbn=0-89820-117-9|ref=harv|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/joelwhitburnstopp00whit}}\n*{{cite book|author=Whitburn, Joel|year=2002|title=Top Country Singles, 1944 to 2001: Chart Data Compiled from Billboard's Country Singles Charts, 1944\u20132001|publisher=Record Research, Inc|isbn=978-0-89820-151-2|ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n\n{{Elvis Presley}}\n{{Elvis Presley singles}}\n{{Donny Osmond}}\n{{John Schneider}}\n{{UK best-selling singles (by year) 1952\u20131969}}\n\n[[Category:1926 songs]]\n[[Category:1950 singles]]\n[[Category:1960 singles]]\n[[Category:Elvis Presley songs]]\n[[Category:The Lettermen songs]]\n[[Category:Al Jolson songs]]\n[[Category:Donny Osmond songs]]\n[[Category:John Schneider (screen actor) songs]]\n[[Category:Billboard Hot 100 number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Billboard Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Australia]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Belgium]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Canada]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in South Africa]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Spain]]\n[[Category:UK Singles Chart number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Songs about loneliness]]\n[[Category:Songs with lyrics by Roy Turk]]\n[[Category:Music published by Bourne Co. Music Publishers]]\n[[Category:Helen Shapiro songs]]\n[[Category:RCA Victor singles]]\n[[Category:Pop ballads]]\n